            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/1319210/">不淫叫，也不思考——看《一声叹息》</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1319210_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1319210">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        中国爱情片在进入2000年后直接进入了神经错乱期，电影导演普遍认为派帅哥美女在银幕上嗲嗲的示爱，搞一些山盟海誓、要死要活、小情小调的爱情就可以糊弄观众。并且自豪的称之为商业片。商业片不是没大脑，不是无视社会现实无病呻吟。我们的没大脑的导演们愚弄观众，疯狂自恋，...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1319210-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1319210_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1319210_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1319210" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1319210">
                                316
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1319210" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1319210">
                                17
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/1319210/#comments" class="reply ">48回应</a>

                    <a href="javascript:;;" class="fold hidden">收起</a>
                </div>
